{% from "components/beach-ball/macro.njk" import beachBall %}

<h2>Default</h2>
<p>{{ beachBall() }}</p>

<h2>Motion</h2>
<p>The beach-ball rotates 360° every 3 seconds. The example CSS
  honours <code>prefers-reduced-motion</code> and disables the
  animation when users prefer reduced motion.</p>

<h2>Accessibility</h2>
<p>The element is always <code>aria-hidden="true"</code> — it is
  purely decorative and screen readers ignore it entirely.</p>
